To update:

1) Make a copy of actual configuration file - phpThumb.config.php to phpThumb.config.php-old
2) Put here the php files, please delete (these are not needed):
cache, demo, docs, fonts, images and also index.php
3) Rename phpThumb.config.php.default to phpThumb.config.php
4) Config phpThumb.config.php, review if it is neccessary the old configuration file and modify as be required
5) Delete phpThumb.config.php-old when you are sure the phpthumb is running ok!
